      "cookedHtml": "<p>We’re thrilled to announce our new widget for <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a>, the <strong>KPI Color Widget</strong>, developed by Caleidos! This intuitive widget allows you to easily visualize key performance indicators with customizable color thresholds to keep your teams aligned and informed.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/3/b/3b58e19639c157ccbbaa78724fb769b7ba3c83a5.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/3/b/3b58e19639c157ccbbaa78724fb769b7ba3c83a5.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"508\" height=\"303\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">678×404 13.8 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/0/c/0c109acb098ab36cc5436abe529043e5d001c08c.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/0/c/0c109acb098ab36cc5436abe529043e5d001c08c_2_492x375.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"492\" height=\"375\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">828×630 16.3 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/wrapped_gift.png?v=14\" title=\":wrapped_gift:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":wrapped_gift:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Exclusive Beta Tester Offer:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Get <strong>6 months FREE</strong> when the widget officially launches!</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/magnifying_glass_tilted_right.png?v=14\" title=\":magnifying_glass_tilted_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":magnifying_glass_tilted_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>What we ask in return:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fill out a short feedback survey.</li>\n<li>Leave an honest review on the <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a> Marketplace upon official launch.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Ready to enhance your dashboards? Join our Beta now: <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_right.png?v=14\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <a href=\"https://forms.monday.com/forms/1fcece3060011e6af1c2f0ec4aa1bff7?r=use1\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Sign up here!</a></p>\n<p>Thanks for helping us shape the future of better KPI management! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/glowing_star.png?v=14\" title=\":glowing_star:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":glowing_star:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>— The Caleidos Team</p>"
